<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.10.8">
<l>cēya ṉaṇiya ṉeṉcin taiyuḷniṉṟa</l>
<l>māyaṉ maṇivā ḷoḷiveṇ ṭaraḷaṅkaḷ</l>
<l>vēyviṇ ṭutirvēṅ kaṭamā malaimēya</l>
<l>vāya ṉaṭiyal latumaṟ ṟaṟiyēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I do not know anything other than the feet of the herder</l>
<l>Who dwells on the great mountain Vēṅkaṭam,</l>
<l>Where jewel[-like], bright, lustrous, white pearls fall from hollow bamboo,</l>
<l>The one who is far, the one who is near, Māyaṉ who remains in my mind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
